{"tid":2260537,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港大通過申作軍和宮鵬出任副校 學生會研採法律行動推翻結果","createTime":"2020-10-27T15:36:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T00:06:34.000Z","uid":240362,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"80dcccc4d6a968d2960d9fbf01538ac02c8a8a09","tid":2260537,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T15:36:40.000Z","msg":"香港大學校委會今日（27日）開會，通過任命清華大學理學院院長宮鵬和清華大學工業工程系系主任兼黨委委員申作軍為副校長。港大學生會會長葉芷琳對結果表示失望和憤怒，認為校委會再一次無視學生的聲音和數千個聯署簽名，表決結果宣告學術和院校自主已經終結：「呢個大學唔係張翔嘅大學，呢度係屬於港大師生嘅大學」，表明不會接受是次結果，未來會諮詢法律意見及後續行動，希望推翻是次表決結果。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201027/JGQECCBUOZBUJK7IQIOIVQAEAQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201027%2FJGQECCBUOZBUJK7IQIOIVQAEAQ%2F&d=BCqMRPjRs%2BrlYbPtDS4RDM%2BSO5qySt9BI5W58Aqq%2Fug%3D&h=281e4e9d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201027%2FJGQECCBUOZBUJK7IQIOIVQAEAQ%2F&h=b4bcd373\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201027/JGQECCBUOZBUJK7IQIOIVQAEAQ/</a>"},{"pid":"649e9c3e567601fad150b08980812798def7e542","tid":2260537,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T15:42:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50229c089cdf82647579b61b970119c358626757","tid":2260537,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T15:43:52.000Z","msg":"有話中共黨員唔可以做副校長?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9974fb2a8a5864c6ac25b7ba2b50aee2230a8c58","tid":2260537,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T15:45:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji